<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pollute-vt">pollute <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pə'luːt/    美 /pə'luːt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>弄脏；污染：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the polluted air 
被污染的空气</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Cars use fuels which pollute the environment very <strong>badly</strong>.
汽车使用严重污染环境的燃料</p><footer>外 研③ – 5改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The river has been polluted by all kinds of industrial waste. 
这条河已被各种工业废料污染了。</p></div></div>